    "body": "Hello @Aboudjem \r\n\r\n32 gas is really nothing here. A safeTransferFrom cost something like 70k gas, so its about 0.05%. On the otherhand doing the proposed change could break any contract where `safeTransferFrom(address, address, uint256, bytes)` is overriden.\r\n\r\nIf someone overrides `safeTransferFrom(address, address, uint256, bytes)`, the changes that he/she adds affect both functions. With your change, you would have to override twice, which some people might forget.",
